Ruckes. A
</taxonomicName>
, B, head, lateral view, 
<taxonomicName id="C7EC4D71FFF1235BFE90F836FEB1F870" box="[278,380,1932,1953]" class="Insecta" family="Pentatomidae" genus="Moncus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hoplita">
