</taxonomicName>
holotype male respectively. C, D, head and pronotum, dorsal plane of the head, 
<taxonomicName id="C7EC4D71FFF1235BFF56F810FEF9F86E" box="[208,308,1962,1983]" class="Insecta" family="Pentatomidae" genus="Moncus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hoplita">
